<% provide(:title, 'City on a Hill - Retreat 2018') %>
<div class="yf-retreat-header-block">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="large-12 columns">
      <img src="http://d3krmhcqjnbsob.cloudfront.net/retreat/2018_retreat_header.jpg" />
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="large-12 columns">
      <div class="yf-retreat-heading center">
        <h1>January 12th - 14th<br>Frontier Camp <span>&#183;</span> Grapeland, TX</h1>
        <h1 id="price">Cost: $90</h1>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<hr />
<div class="yf-retreat-theme-block center">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="large-12 columns">
      <h1>Theme: City on a Hill</h1>
      <h4>Matthew 5:14-16</h4>
      <p><i>"You are the light of the world. A town built on a hill cannot be hidden. Neither do people light a lamp and put it under a bowl. Instead they put it on its stand, and it gives light to everyone in the house. In the same way, let your light shine before others, that they may see your good deeds and glorify your Father in heaven."</i></p>
      <h3>Speaker: Alex Mathew</h3>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>
<hr />
<div class="yf-retreat-payment-methods-block">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="large-12 columns">
      <div class="center">
        <h1>Ways to Pay</h1>
        <h4>There are three simple ways to pay for retreat this year!</h4>
      </div>
      <p><span>Online:</span> You can make a payment online with a credit card using the form below.</p><br>
      <p><span>In-person:</span> You can pay in-person with cash or check. Just find a YF officer to make your payment.</p><br>
      <p><span>Venmo:</span> If you would like to use Venmo, select "Venmo" as your payment method in the form below and we will send you a payment request on there! Easy! <br>Our Venmo ID: @TMC-YF</p><br>
      <div class="yf-retreat-payment-methods-important center">
        <p>NOTE: RETREAT PRICE WILL INCREASE TO $100 AFTER DECEMBER 31ST, 2017. NO EXCEPTIONS.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<hr />
<!-- <div class="yf-retreat-schedule-block center">
  <h1>Schedule</h1>
  <h4>- TBA -</h4>
</div>
<hr /> -->
<div class="yf-retreat-form-block">
  <h1 class="center">Registration Form</h1>
  <%= render 'form' %>
</div>
<hr />
<div class="yf-retreat-payment-block center">
<h1>Online Payment</h1>
<%= form_tag retreat_charge_path do %>
    <label class="amount">
      <h5>Amount: $90</h5>
      <p>Please use the same email as on the registration form!<br><em>There will be a convenience charge of $3.00 applied.<em></p>
    </label>
    <script
      src="https://checkout.stripe.com/checkout.js" class="stripe-button"
      data-key=<%= ENV['STRIPE_PUBLIC_KEY'] %>
      data-image="http://d3krmhcqjnbsob.cloudfront.net/sitelogo.png"
      data-name="Retreat 2018: City on a Hill"
      data-description="1 golden ticket ($93)"
      data-amount="9300">
    </script>
  <% end %>
</div>
